Description of incident: Emergence Health Network has notified patients of a data breach to their system when a server was accessed without authorization.  "It is not apparent that any medical information was disclosed based  upon a third-party audit of the computer server and EHN does not have  any proof that information such as social security number, date of  birth, home address, was accessed or otherwise misused"More information: http://emergencehealthnetwork.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/EHN-Compute...
